Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:06.67,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(686,614)}AOI-YA{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyottoko, Beshimi, Shikijo, Han'nya...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:57.15,Style 2,,0,0,60,,{\an8\i1\c&H4225A6&\3c&HFFFFFF&}RUROUNIKEN SHIN\NNEW KYOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have you carved one\Nthat you find agreeable?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot picture the face of a\NBuddha that will save our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just use my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What inscription would go with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Those who are strong live;\Nthose who are weak die."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Although crude,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps the more basic a concept is,\Nthe closer it draws to the ultimate truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuji again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mastering one's powers is\Nhardly an easy task, Anji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Usui's grave, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are most kind, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to mourn the loss\Nof someone who dared to defy Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, each one of us, was originally\Nkilled by what we call the Meiji Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In our own ways, we were persecuted by\Nthe era and stripped of our reasons to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we were able to find the\Nlight by serving Master Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Light? Even though Shishio\Nruined both of Usui's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire to take revenge upon\NMaster Shishio was Usui's very reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that could be light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, our ship will sail to glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.73,Style 2,,0,0,60,,{\an8\i1}WARBLE OF LIGHT{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.77,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(466,132)}KYOTO{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.77,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(330,490)}OSAKA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.77,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(882,588)}IGA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Battle of Toba-Fushimi\Nin the Boshin War,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshinobu Tokugawa fled to Edo\Nby boat from the Port of Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.49,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(156,262)}HAMAE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.43,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(612,258)}OWARI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.43,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(876,302)}MIKAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.43,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1148,350)}TOTOMI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His actions played a large role\Nin the loyalist army's victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shishio is taking an ironic approach and\Nturning their cause of victory into his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.88,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,104)}SAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.88,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(270,248)}SURUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.88,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,342)}IZU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,his true target lies to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.52,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,110)}MUSASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.52,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,110)}TOKYO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.52,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,324)}SURUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He is going after-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the person over there, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:24.63,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(548,136)}CAFETERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:24.63,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1168,496)}OCCUPATIONAL\NHEALTH\NMANAGEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to Kyoto on your own\Nwithout food or water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, how pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First that girl and now you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am amazed how you hold that\Nman in such high regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come all the way to Kyoto\Njust to give Kenshin a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Thanks fer waitin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to fight my own battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate anyone that does something\Nas cowardly as stabbing another in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a Sekiho Army soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never bring myself to\Nforgive the Meiji government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They dirtied my master's name by calling\Nhim a traitor and then killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he plays dirty in his fight against the\Ngovernment and involves innocent lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes him no different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna hunt Shishio down,\Nit'll go faster if I stick with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Captain of the\NShinsengumi's 3rd Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did nothing I said enter those\Nears of yours, Bird Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in fully enjoying the\Ntaste of my rice when I'm eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Saito's information, Shishio\Nis headed there to carry out his secret plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make the Great Kyoto Fire a bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He has invested the majority\Nof his subordinates in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He has something so powerful that he\Ncould still win with a small group of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How's that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance... a black ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A black ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was merely an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tokyo is still scared by the\Narrival of the black ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If what appeared to be a battleship\Nwere to drop anchor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that alone would inevitably create turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you decide to\Ntell us about all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kept my silence, well...\NI feared you may do something rash...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for being a rash woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief! Did you come all of the way\Nto Kyoto for a lover's quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}I rashly followed you all of the way to Kyoto!\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Good grief! Did you come all of the way\Nto Kyoto for a lover's quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, stop! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A messenger pigeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lu No. 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kenshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:07.02,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(870,348)}AOI-YA{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry to impose at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is fine. We have some spare rooms anyway.\NStay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? It was Aoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aoshi... was no longer\Nthe Master Aoshi I once knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where justice lies,\Nbut I don't care about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to defeat Master Aoshi,\Nno, Aoshi Shinomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoshi Shinomori, why have you\Ndecided to join us in arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That man claimed he would prepare a stage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,where I may face Himura Battousai\Nin our final battle without interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here for that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Soujiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited him to serve as a\Nreplacement for Chou and Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that uncalled for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who has obtained Shakku's\Nfinal piece may indeed come after us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but he is not the one I am after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall leave that man to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You may perform a spectacular opening act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! From this moment on,\NI am the head of the Oniwabanshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shishio and his men will use the\Nchaos created by the fires to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like all of you to prevent\Nany casualties in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, but what about Shishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to shoulder it\Non your own again, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stay and help Misao in the fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So... let's be sure we go back\Nto Tokyo together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear in mind what will happen if you dare\Nto break your promise with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Missh Haoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't mind them. They're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that, Kenshin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so obvious, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If Himura were in the wrong,\Nhe would not have someone who loves him so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aoshi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll swap with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to protect Kyoto together.\NDoesn't that make us friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that easy to become\Nfriends with someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is quite difficult to earn a person's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, what would it take to earn your trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Why don't we spar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,During a sword fight,\Nyou learn how the other feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. This isn't the time for that, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, I mean. It's like you're inept, or...\Nmaybe you'd call it "sassy."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda feels like you're speaking\Nstraight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura trusted and relied on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Himura and I trust you and the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight together! Guard duty starts tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuro, Shiro, Masu-Kami, Omime,\Neveryone, get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oniwabanshu moves out tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko, please take care of Kyoto...\Nand Miss Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! This is my chance to show how\Ngreat the Kamiya Kasshin-ryuu is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! I had a message for you, Kenshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from that geezer, Hiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiko? Seijuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has finally obtained what he{\i}\N{\i1}once lacked with the sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that mean?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If all you do is slice each other's flesh,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you have not truly crossed swords{\i}\N{\i1}with your opponent.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the sword, you must touch{\i}\N{\i1}your opponent's heart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise, you cannot threaten your foe's{\i}\N{\i1}life in the true meaning of the word.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Mind, skill and body."{\i}\N{\i1}All martial arts share this concept.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In swordsmanship, you use the sword to{\i}\N{\i1}learn about your foe as well as yourself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is essential that it comes from the heart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the sword,\Nyou must touch your opponent's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin, was that drunken geezer really your...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my master. Thank you, Yahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have done a fine job\Ndelivering the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, will Kyoto be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently a man from Tokyo named Fujita\Nrounded up 5,000 police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I appreciate what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ones to protect Kyoto will be us,\Nthe onmitsu Oniwabanshu! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's ready for a fight!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sou! Quit ogling the ship\Nand give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You said to carve "Survival of the Fittest," into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, when you lose your life,\Nthis Buddhist statue will cease to speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It will transform into a puppet\Nstained with falsehoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that meant as encouragement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, as a provocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph... You fallen monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this taking a while? We should\Nbe able to see the fires in Kyoto by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They are up against 5,000 police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only natural for them to run into problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the soldiers might be bailing out on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be unforgivable!\NHow dare they betray Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They may flee if they so wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But would they truly do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They already know; there is nowhere\Nin this country for them to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is precisely why they chose to follow me.\NIt's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They may betray me for all I care.\NEach of them has his own battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the blazes begun to soar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.\NThere is a carriage headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, one of them is spewing out steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the one? It doesn't look\Nlike a massive black ship to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just as I had anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bird brain may not understand,\Nbut that is called "camouflage."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It means appearances can\Ndeceive a bunch of morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! False security makes for a fierce enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A survivor from the Shinsengumi\Nhas come to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad it wasn't the one you longed for, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how to go about attacking a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never make it if we swam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I will be forced to pray\Nfor your souls once you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I am not a devout believer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel somewhat uncomfortable\Nwith fighting a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, leave this lug to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it,\Nhe doesn't have a weapon on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a fistfight, then it's right up my alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he is all yours, but don't take him lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! False security's dangerous and fire's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You're one destructive monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early in the year\Nfor swimming in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito sure is trying his hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use "that." Sou, give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. It will fire once you turn the lever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now breach the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hajime Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou, load her with more ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That is enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If one of the last surviving Shinsengumi\Ngot shot and became fish food,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it would mortify him on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall face him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shishio's actions are never\Ncontradictory, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Subsequently leaving us with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes things easy, doesn't it, Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard my vessel, Hajime Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you.\NI call myself Makoto Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My subordinates gave you a rude welcoming,\Nbut for coming to see me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to show my\Nappreciation with this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It would appear you possess\Nthe prowess needed to bind a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, I shall fight you\Nwith all of my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Did you two do this? I called for the police,\Nso let them bind these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Misa-er, the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-er, the boss is doing\Na good job directing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've caught just about all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should drop by the Aoi-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-er, Boss, thanks to civilian assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we were able to extinguish\Nall of the fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did pretty good for my first job, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great how we were able to protect Kyo-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Lu No. 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on fire?! The Aoi-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, you are powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good eye when appraising you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My greatest obstacle is indeed you,\NHajime Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I am also disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wield such power, so why has one\Nwho was once called a Wolf of Mibu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered himself to serving as\Na government dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this era satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A defanged wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What would possibly make you\Nwag your tail for this era?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill. Evil. Instantly."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill. Evil. Instantly"? Am I evil? What is evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In my eyes, raw power is justice.\NWeakness is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito, your strength comes from your conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are different from Battousai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us see whose beliefs are right.\NBear your fangs and howl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gatotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem we've found our answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You were close, but once a wolf has lost his\Nfangs, he is little different from a cur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there are no obstacles standing in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi, increase the engine's power.\NUpon Anji's arrival, we set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito, I shall bring you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you the evil\NMeiji government's demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou, treat his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.52,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(800,420)}AOI- YA{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko, we'll strike at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off of his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochika, look after Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you monks could be so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of your skills,\Nwhy do you serve under Shishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I may have fallen, I am still a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I am unable to\Nbelieve in God or Buddha,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I require a subject to pray to\Nor I will no longer even be a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if Makoto Shishio\Nis some higher being or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't let you create a world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,where we worship scum who're blind\Nto the pain of the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give this my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Yes, sir! I am on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks to my head guard.\NAre we still waiting for Anji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito's companion is giving him a hard time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We will wait a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem the "boss"\Nis still waiting for his man as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Sou here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I am going to cool down my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In this era that deliriously cries "peace,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had lost the ability to see my true dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one man who shows me\Na dream from which I shall never wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito, you sure are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that move called Gatotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment, I thought you had won.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you recover from those wounds,\Nplease fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Himura I'd fight him,\Nso it would have to come after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but only if you defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. You hold Himura in\Nhigh regard, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am sure that's only natural since you've\Nbeen rivals since the end of the Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've crossed blades with him,\Nthen you should already know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be rather dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to fight him again, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has finally made his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiko, get back! Yahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin left this place in our care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to take a single step back!\NI can't pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yahiko, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.67,0:24:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the end of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, so it was a sakabatou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakabatou: A sword that cannot kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:24:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakku must have wavered clear to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.79,0:25:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the strong will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.10,0:25:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so simple, and yet he failed to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.63,0:25:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a defective sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.70,0:25:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an appropriate sword for you,\Nwho always hesitate to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not cast aside my hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.67,0:25:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who I have met\Nprecisely because of that hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijuro Hiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.65,0:25:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You left before I was done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.15,0:25:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.92,0:25:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to repay me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.16,0:25:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to work hard to cover\Nthe cost of the pot you broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.96,0:25:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you going on about\Nat a time like this, Geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem your debt is about to grow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A massive body filled with too much power...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.77,0:25:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to master his own strength,\Nhe must have suffered under that armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.68,0:25:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart does not wish to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.11,0:25:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,yet he finds himself unable to resist\Nhis natural instinct to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.12,0:25:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to Shishio,\Nwho had accepted that about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.72,0:26:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall put your suffering to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.02,0:26:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you will find a man whom you\Ncannot defeat, even at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me! Let me see the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.29,0:26:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.01,0:26:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your new sword is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.91,0:26:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are even able to\Nkeep up with my speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.15,0:27:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right when you you are\Nno longer the Battousai, Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.12,0:27:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword and katana that cannot kill\Nshouldn't be this powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.32,0:27:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What Saito said is also eating at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not want to acknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hesitation must never defeat conviction!\NIt must not!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.33,0:27:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight for keeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can win! I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.92,0:27:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.86,0:27:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you lacked emotions,\NI was unable to predict your moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.10,0:27:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.20,0:27:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura, you used your sword\Nto read my emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.17,0:28:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost, for you have awoken my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.21,0:28:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You now possess a different power from\Nthe one you wielded in your Battousai days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be dense, but now I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that will not work on Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.05,0:28:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shishio burns through life without\Na breadth of hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart is the color of a black flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.86,0:28:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.10,0:28:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijuro Hiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw through that monstrous\Nman's misery as a warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.87,0:28:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,having never known what it meant\Nto feel fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.94,0:28:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a fearsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.21,0:28:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Misery as a warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.28,0:28:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The same is also true of Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.15,0:28:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who has gathered under Shishio
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.85,0:28:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,has been left at the mercy\Nof the patriotic extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.39,0:28:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They have been hurt in both body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.16,0:28:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is precisely why they depend on strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.99,0:28:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They depend on power.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.83,0:28:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.36,0:28:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.84,0:29:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Light? Is that how you guys\Nview Makoto Shishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.41,0:29:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Monks must always seek salvation for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.05,0:29:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would do anything to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.45,0:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll find salvation\Nbeyond destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.98,0:29:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what the Shinto and Buddhist\Ngods want, then it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.25,0:29:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But humans have no right to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.92,0:29:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never accept your salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.33,0:29:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.21,0:29:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.35,0:29:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell, when we throw our punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.08,0:29:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.42,0:29:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.39,0:29:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In Shishio's eyes, you are the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:29:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He is searching for salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.03,0:30:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto Shishio... does not\Nyearn for his own salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.97,0:30:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to be the burning flame\Nthat will arouse the era.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He would use himself as the tinder...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.24,0:30:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Makoto Shishio will...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.98,0:30:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask: What is your light?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.25,0:30:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My light?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I felt despair for the era\Nand had given up, a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.02,0:30:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...made me decide to believe\Nin the future once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.97,0:30:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This signal indicates that Master Shishio\Nis setting sail for glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.41,0:30:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.44,0:30:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.24,0:30:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.15,0:30:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto Shishio once said, "Our world is Hell."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.02,0:31:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,While in Hell, he would don the flames of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and thrust forward with a large ironclad warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.09,0:31:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It-it's a black ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.53,0:31:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.16,0:31:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...is {\i1}Purgatory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.14,0:31:18.57,Style 1,,0,0,60,,{\an8}PURGATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.57,0:31:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Purgatory...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.24,0:31:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to {\i1}Purgatory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.44,0:31:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to {\i1}Purgatory.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.01,0:31:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You downed Soujiro using\NShakku's last sword? Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.05,0:31:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had prepared an opening act for you, but it\Nwould seem you have already been wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.45,0:31:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we skip to the main show: a battle\Nbetween brother swords, my predecessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.99,0:31:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's. That is why I have come... with this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.16,0:31:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship has left port.\NLet's go all the way to Tokyo together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reach Tokyo, which of our\Ncorpses will have taken the helm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.18,0:31:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have the face of a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.38,0:32:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched... that man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.38,0:32:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,His heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.08,0:32:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Infinite Blade, Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.05,0:32:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the name Shakku bequeathed this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.59,0:32:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite; it promises unending victory\Nno matter where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.36,0:32:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sakabatou, Keishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.33,0:32:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword is the embodiment\Nof how Master Shakku felt in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.30,0:32:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the equinox of his revelation was\Na hell on earth that tumbles in bloody mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.51,0:32:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenshin, will you be able to{\i}\N{\i1}touch Makoto Shishio's heart?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.10,0:33:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate to say it, but you cannot defeat me\Nwith a sakabatou, my predecessor!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.41,0:33:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword is a tool used for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.11,0:33:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hope to defeat me, reverse your blade\Nand become the Battousai once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.48,0:33:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not reverse my blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.49,0:33:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,not so long as this sword takes the form of\Nan earnest desire for an age of peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.39,0:33:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot change the world through ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.19,0:33:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You will only be devoured by the\Nlaw of "Survival of the Fittest."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.24,0:33:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So they made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.41,0:33:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjust the angle for error!\NLoad the next cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.58,0:33:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00FFFF&}Officer Saito, don't die!{\i}\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00FFFF&}Officer Saito, don't die!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.35,0:33:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let that ship leave the bay! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those government dogs\Nare putting up a decent fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.13,0:33:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi, change course.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.36,0:33:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The bombardment is\Nmost likely coming from Mt. Tenpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.20,0:33:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence them with a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.47,0:34:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise the angle of projection a little.\NKeep this position!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.14,0:34:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Four, three, two! Commence fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.35,0:34:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't falter! Continue firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.54,0:34:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo will share the same fate.\NSuch is {\i1}Purgatory's{\i} power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.65,0:34:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Engine Room. The cannons\Nare making the engine gush steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.69,0:34:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The high temperatures prevent\Nus from approaching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.79,0:34:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.79,0:35:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My predecessor, it must be karma for\Nthe terrible things we have done,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.69,0:35:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because we never seem to have\Nmuch luck when it matters most!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.67,0:35:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you feel what makes me boil,\Nmy predecessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.55,0:35:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if your swords touch one another's hearts,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.62,0:35:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you cannot win if your{\i}\N{\i1}opponent devours your heart.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you win, Kenshin?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The light...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.26,0:36:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.36,0:36:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He touched his opponent's\Nheart through his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.87,0:36:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenshin...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.84,0:36:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Abandon ship! Evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.39,0:36:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.39,0:36:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On a sinking ship where\Neveryone is about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.46,0:36:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,no one will come to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.60,0:36:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we shall hold our final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.50,0:36:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, I have lost my friends...\NI have lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.70,0:36:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat you and decorate their tombstones
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.58,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with the flower called "the title of strongest."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.78,0:36:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have not lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.48,0:37:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a young lady who adores you\Nand hopes to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked by that very young lady...\Nto defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.36,0:37:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have touched his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.59,0:37:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would this have turned out differently, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.73,0:37:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have touched Master Aoshi's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot grant Miss Misao's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.80,0:37:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring Aoshi Shinomori\Nback home to Miss Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.61,0:37:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, there is the Aoshi Shinomori\Nbefore me who writhes in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.45,0:37:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I must slice away the these delusions that\NMiss Misao hates with my sakabatou, Keishin!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.79,0:37:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.62,0:37:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.76,0:37:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the fire reaches the armory,\Nthis ship will be dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.56,0:37:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to be gone before then,\Nbut I can't row the boat with my legs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.53,0:37:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to take me to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.93,0:37:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.85,0:38:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.96,0:38:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.51,0:38:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shishio, look. It is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.41,0:38:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our world is burning so brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.49,0:38:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has proceeded just as\Nyou wished, Master Shishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.90,0:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumi, you're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the only one who got left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.77,0:39:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Saito, I blame you! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The black ship, {\i1}Purgatory,{\i} is sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.65,0:39:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.85,0:39:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have protected Tokyo. Next comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.61,0:39:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, this was the only place\Nthat got hit by the Great Kyoto Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.55,0:39:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that the damage\Nwas minimal! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.68,0:39:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not great!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.82,0:39:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.08,0:39:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.56,0:40:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.83,0:40:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.11,0:40:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.58,0:40:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.08,0:40:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.79,0:40:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where did\Nthat geezer Hiko go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.53,0:40:34.79,Style 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,434)}ELIXIR
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.66,0:40:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will party again tonight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.58,0:41:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Infinite Blade, Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.02,0:41:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as my father dreamed of an age of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.02,0:41:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he continued to forge swords meant to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.13,0:41:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword that most strongly represents\Nhis contradiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...shall be sealed here as an offering to the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.74,0:41:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.81,0:41:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I would like for you to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.84,0:41:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My father placed all of his\Nfeelings into that sakabatou.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.18,0:41:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure that you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.72,0:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would be most grateful\Nif you let me borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.92,0:41:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.62,0:41:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In a world of true peace, even a\Nsakabatou will become unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.96,0:41:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor will there be a need declare\Nthat I will not take one's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.20,0:41:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When such a world comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.13,0:41:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I would like to\Nhumbly lay down the sword
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.87,0:41:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and place this sakabatou next to Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.11,0:41:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Humbwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Humbly?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.18,0:41:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He means Himura!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.71,0:42:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Humbwee! Humbwee! Himura ish humbwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.85,0:42:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Kaketa kotae ga ikutsu mo aru no\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Several answers have left me wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.73,0:42:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Tadashisa dake ja tarinai\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Simply being correct is not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.90,0:43:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Futatsu kasanete mita kedo, chigatta yo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}I tried overlapping two, but it wasn't right
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.98,0:43:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.78,0:43:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Mitasarete mieru keshiki wa yasashii\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}The seemingly satisfied view is gentle
