Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.07,0:43:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Kieteshimau na yo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Never disappear on me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.03,0:43:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Atarashii ibuki yo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Give voice to your
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.97,0:43:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Koe ni dashite hibikasete\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}New breath of life and let it ring
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.75,0:43:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Furesasete ite yo\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Let me touch you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}Tada hitori kokoro ubawareta\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}You are the only one to steal my heart
